ActNational Security and Intelligence Review Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of CHARLES FUGÈRE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Executive Director of the National Security and Intelligence Review Agency Secretariat on an interim basis, for a term of eight months or until such time as a new Executive Director is appointed, whichever occurs first.
